::DarkMouse::

She looks around and doesn't see the rat.  She takes a chance and 
runs for it.  She dodges trees and jumps over a small creek.  She 
keeps going as fast as she can.  She wasn't one who delt with these 
situations well. She muttered to herself while running,"What am I 
doing here? I'm a tech mouse.  I do computer work and fix systems. 
I'm no fighter."  She felt a jolt of energy run through her memory 
banks.  She started to remember things from a long time ago.
She remembered when she was a predacon and changing into a maximal. 
She remembered a huge spider trying to kill her.  She remembered a 
strange bot, part scorpion and snake, who was kind to her.  She 
remembered a scorpion bot who was something dear to her.  She shook 
her head to clear it of her thoughts and kept running.
